OL,3,CNew report calls for eight-week break
OL,4,Cand mid-season rest for footballers
OL,6,FAll professional footballers must be
OL,7,Fgiven at least eight weeks to rest and
OL,8,Fretrain between seasons and a minimum
OL,9,Fone-week mid-season break, according
OL,10,Fto a new report.
OL,12,FThe call for minimum protections to be
OL,13,Fintroduced worldwide comes as some of
OL,14,Fthe world's top stars including
OL,15,FManchester City prepare to take part
OL,16,Fin the newly-expanded FIFA Club World
OL,17,FCup in the United States, which begins
OL,18,Fon Saturday 14 June.
