OL,6,FThe tournament does not end until 13
OL,7,FJuly, meaning Manchester City and
OL,8,FChelsea players could have a gap of
OL,9,Fjust five weeks before the new Premier
OL,10,FLeague season kicks off on 16 August.
OL,12,FThat is two weeks less than the
OL,13,Fminimum off-season rest and retraining
OL,14,Fperiod a group of 70 medical and
OL,15,Fperformance experts have recommended
OL,16,Fin a new study.
