OL,4,Cand mid-season rest for footballers
OL,6,FEngland head coach Thomas Tuchel said
OL,7,Fearlier this week that the demands
OL,8,Fplaced on City and Chelsea by the Club
OL,9,FWorld Cup will hand a "huge advantage"
OL,10,Fto Liverpool and Arsenal in next
OL,11,Fseason's Premier League title race.
OL,13,FThe European division of world
OL,14,Fplayers' union FIFPRO and Europe's
OL,15,Fleagues have taken legal action
OL,16,Fagainst FIFA over what they see as a
OL,17,Flack of consultation by the game's
OL,18,Fglobal governing body over the fixture
OL,19,Fcalendar.
