OL,6,FThe scheduling of the Club World Cup
OL,7,Fwithin that calendar has been
OL,8,Fdescribed as a "tipping point" in the
OL,9,Fdebate by Premier League chief
OL,10,Fexecutive Richard Masters.
OL,12,FThe expert group has put forward 12
OL,13,F'position statements' on player
OL,14,Fwelfare as part of the Delphi Study,
OL,15,Fwhich they feel should be adopted
OL,16,Fworldwide as minimum welfare standards.
