OL,3,CNew report calls for eight-week break
OL,4,Cand mid-season rest for footballers
OL,6,FThese included a mandatory four-week
OL,7,Foff-season break, and within that a
OL,8,Ftwo-week blackout period where clubs
OL,9,Fand national teams should have no
OL,10,Fcontact at all with players.
OL,12,FThere should then be a minimum four-
OL,13,Fweek retraining period after the off-
OL,14,Fseason break before resuming
OL,15,Fcompetitive football.
OL,17,FMid-season breaks should last a
OL,18,Fminimum of one week, experts
OL,19,Fsaid.Premier League players will not
OL,20,Fbenefit from any mid-season break next
OL,21,Fseason, as was the case in 2024-25.
