OL,6,FA pause was introduced in the 2019-20
OL,7,Fseason but was dropped before the
OL,8,Fstart of the season just ended, due to
OL,9,Fthe expansion of international
OL,10,Fcompetitions like UEFA's Champions
OL,11,FLeague, Europa League and Conference
OL,12,FLeague.
OL,14,FThe 12 position statements were agreed
OL,15,Fwith the consensus of at least 75 per
OL,16,Fcent of the experts involved.
