OL,3,CNew report calls for eight-week break
OL,4,Cand mid-season rest for footballers
OL,6,FAmong the other statements were calls
OL,7,Ffor mandatory consideration of the
OL,8,Ftravel burden on players and the
OL,9,Fimpact of long-haul flights, as well
OL,10,Fas specific workload safeguards for
OL,11,Funder-18 players.
OL,13,FDr Vincent Gouttebarge, the medical
OL,14,Fdirector of FIFPRO, said: "This study
OL,15,Fpresents safety standards based on the
OL,16,Fconsidered and independent opinions of
OL,17,Fmedical and performance experts
OL,18,Fworking in professional football who
OL,19,Funderstand the mental and physical
OL,20,Fstrain placed on players.
